Tail Lash				KEY:Companion (Dinosaur (Diplodocus)) ~ Tail Lash			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Extraordinary							DESC:The diplodocus prefers to attack with its tail. The dinosaur can snap its incredibly long tail with surprising speed like an enormous whip-this is a primary attack that deals bludgeoning and slashing damage. A diplodocus can make two separate attacks with its tail lash as a full-attack action.		BONUS:WEAPONPROF=Tail Slap|TOHIT|5		BONUS:WEAPONPROF=Tail Slap|DAMAGE|STR/2
